CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 25, 1962, pg. 23 reads: "Planning Gala Loendi Week - Members of the program committee for Loendi Week, Sept. 9-15, are, left to right, seated: Sue Corsey, Margaret Hipkins, Fred Gladney, chairman; Pauline Sotts, Lenora Rainey, Virginia Williams, Margarette Burton and Thelma Sales. Standing: Otto Simonson, Harry Richards, Dorothy Paige, Ralph Mellix Jr., Anne Hardaway, John Burton and Adam Wilson. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Loendi Week program committee members, seated, left to right: Sue Corsey, Margaret Hipkins, Fred Gladney, Pauline Sotts, Lenora Rainey, Virginia Williams, Margarette Burton, and Thelma Sales; standing, left to right: Otto Simonson, Harry Richards, Dorothy Paige, Ralph Mellix Jr., Anne Hardaway, John Burton, and Adam Wilson, gathered around table in Loendi Club with sunburst clock
